data.meta_description:
Be a Hero For a Better World - DoOneThing.org - A project of The EMILY Fund. Featuring more than 5000 FREE printable
resources on more than 60 social issues. Do One Thing for a Better World - every act of compassion
makes a difference!  Portraits of Heroes for a Better World are included for illustration purposes only. No celebrity endorsement is implied.
